Package: WOTPLY
Type: Package
Title: Plot connectivity between cells from different time points starting from Waddington-OT output
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Gabriele Lubatti
Maintainer: Gabriele Lubatti <gabriele.lubatti@helmholtz-muenchen.de>
Description: R package that shows the connections between selected clusters from the latest time point and the clusters from all the previous time points. The transition matrices between time point t and t+1 are obtained from Waddington-OT analysis.
License:  GPL-3
Depends:
    R (>= 4.0)
Imports:
    network,
    GGally
Suggests:
    testthat,
    knitr
VignetteBuilder: 
    knitr
biocViews: software
BugReports: https://github.com/ScialdoneLab/WOTPLY/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.1.1
